Protein World diet supplements is facing a massive backlash over its billboard campaign . 
  It features a svelte bikini-clad model asking 'Are you beach body ready?' More than 50,000 people have signed a petition to have them removed . 
  Many posters have been vandalised with feminist slogans . 
  Marketing boss Richard Staveley said the company has received bomb threats . 
  He said the campaign was 'brilliant' and that he didn't see the company changing . 
 